#
# PHILOSOPHY: Historical reports are generated by running the REAL pipeline
# (change_miner → ci_mapper → env_classifier → impact_graph) against mock data.
# Only impact_analyzer (LLM) is bypassed — replaced with pre-written mock impact
# that matches what Gemini would say. This means:
#   - Report structure is IDENTICAL to live pipeline output
#   - Historical RAG search returns meaningful, consistent results
#   - No LLM quota is burned generating historical data
#   - Delete reports/ and re-run this script any time to refresh

